#### PR description:

The goal of this PR is a heavy refactoring of the package `CondTools/SiPixel`, as a follow-up of https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/35495.
   * plugin files have now class declarations within the implementation `.cc` file (headers are removed);
   * generalized modernization of the code where possible;
   * commit 4f580dd77814101f0ae0749fc758bdd16237af46 migrates away from the deprecated `CondCore.DBCommon.CondDBCommon_cfi` includes;
   * commit faa6ea2071132845aa04c770138f211475697e29 reduces the verbosity of CPE uploader configuration codes which were clogging the unit test logs.

#### PR validation:

Relies on existing unit tests.

